               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾaślǝṭi, Lectionary for the entire year (fols. 5ra-51rb)
                     
 Colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="5ra" to="67ra"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1917Mashaf#year">Maṣḥafa ʾaślǝṭi, Lectionary for the entire year</title>
                     <textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#3ra">3ra</locus> ... መጽሐፈ፡ አስልጥ፡ ...<note>The text is called ʾaslǝṭ in the incipit. </note></incipit>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1"><locus target="#51va"/> ይትባረከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አምላከ፡ አበውየ፡ ዘአፈጸመኒ፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፈ፡
                        በዳህና፡ ወበሰላም። ተጽሕፈ፡ በ፲፻ወ፱፻፳ <cb/> ፪፡ ዓመት፡ እምልደተ፡
                        እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በዘመነ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ወንጉሥነ፡ ኃይለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወጳጳስነ። <note>The colophon mentions
                        the date <date notBefore="1929" notAfter="1930">1922 A.M. (=1929/30 A.D.)</date> and King Ḫāyla Śǝllāse I (r. <date>1930-1974</date>).</note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                 
